abstract: >-
  GUI-based Python framework for hierarchical and replicate-aware
  statistical analysis of biological datasets using stratified
  nonparametric testing and linear mixed-effects models.

keywords:
  - "hierarchical statistics"
  - "linear mixed model"
  - "stratified Wilcoxon"
  - "van Elteren"
  - "biostatistics"
  - "replicate-aware analysis"
  - "mixed-effects modeling"
